description: The 15.4" MacBook Pro Laptop Computer with Retina Display from Apple is a powerful notebook computer with an innovative, ultrathin, ultraportable aluminum unibody design.
This powerful laptop includes a 10th gen i7-10750H processor,  16GB RAM and a 512GB SSD+1TB HDD.
Featuring Apple's 64-bit A8X chip and M8 coprocessor, the Air 2 delivers 40% faster CPU performance and 2.5 times the graphics performance when compared to its predecessor.
